        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "We're planning on releasing 0.6 in a couple weeks, and technically in \"feature freeze\" mode right now. If you want to lead this I would consider merging it before the 0.7 cycle, but informally I think we're targeting around a 6 month release cycle (pending roadmap discussions). That being said I would like to redesign the interface around start_client which I think is likely going to be hard to do/approve before 0.6. Of course I only speak for me :) \r\n\r\nI'm focused right now on ensuring our multibyte handling is correct because I think that's a more pressing issue. ",
